Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:57.11,Sora Eng dialogue,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You've become so good at it now, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:03.88,Sora Eng dialogue,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I am so happy! Even Rio-senpai's been praising me recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:11.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you joined the army because you wanted to play the trumpet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:13.58,Sora Eng dialogue,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.05,Sora Eng dialogue,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,What is your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:23.30,Sora Eng dialogue,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,67)}The sound of the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:23.30,Sora Eng dialogue,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:27.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream? Isn't it obvious in your case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be good at the trumpet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But after I said so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:39.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told "It's just a small objective and can't be considered as a dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat Mishio is getting quite pretentious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:48.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't a dream also an objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking because I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:59.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's close and you know clearly how to reach it, it's called "Objective", and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:04.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's faraway and unrealistic, then it's called "Dream", isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unrealistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't you have your own dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have one Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dream shouldn't be easily told to others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have, but it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Rio-senpai have been doing things in secret recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,does that have anything to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an interest, not a... dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why can't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it will disappear if I say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... A dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:57.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it, it's true that I don't have a faraway and unrealistic dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so lonely like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Rio-senpai have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:07.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:17.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, to be good at playing trumpet is already a big objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so anxious to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:33.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give our dreamless lady an objective then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go out for a while, master that music sheet before I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Master it completely, all the way through the third movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a really difficult one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear you playing it when I come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:59.08,Book,File,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz326.354\pos(931,131)\c&H000000&\3c&H3A3F4B&}Score file
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:06:01.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that for now, I should start with things that I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:14.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... You look different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, perhaps it's because I cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Anyway, I came here with an important letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dedicated letter delivered directly from the Roman Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my first time delivering such kind of mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems that it requires delivery confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:43.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back if the receipt isn't signed. Where's Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it urgent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go fetch her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Klaus-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if I manage to work until my pension,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:03.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning to go back to my hometown and get some big fields to farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those extra large ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:10.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll enjoy my home grown rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:21.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who're always doing delivery work all over the place, like me, usually want to do something of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, what you said was very useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:32.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Kureha-chan is preparing dinner in the canteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:36.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can join us if you'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan would be very glad, I think.
