Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... It's so good to have dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful dreams huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's Kanata-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:08.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio went to the glass factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also searching for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:17.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:22.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father said that the ordered item was completed so he asked me to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:28.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san, why do you work at the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:33.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my dream is to make better artwork than my father and sell it in this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:39.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would put the artwork of a girl who abandoned her home on display to sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cruel, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who chose to learn from that useless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Naomi-san or Onee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:54.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What is the mom stuff and learning stuff all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know Kanata-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:01.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father and Naomi-chan were husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:05.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A poor decision because we were too young and impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fruit of their love is Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.55,Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(361,482,361,655)\fs50\frz337.553\frx342\fry326}Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See! The proof is in this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are asking such a difficult question straight off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should say that our dream differed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:43.59,Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(381,348,381,719)\fs50\frz349.553}Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:41.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing for me was this shop, but in his case, it was making glass works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we couldn't make a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So young at that time... The both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:52.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Their result is Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:00.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care on the road, don't get distracted by the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm entrusting this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:07.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A necklace, the one that the Maiden of Flame use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:16.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the timing, I think I should surely have crossed path with Rio somewhere though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:24.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, maybe Rio is spacing out somewhere on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also pay some attention to the roadside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Maybe I'm worrying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:50.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this year's Maiden of Flame will also be chosen from among the fort citizens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you also heard from Kanata and the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:05.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the Roman girl, Aisha, said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Roman version of the Maidens of Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite concerned, so I did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:18.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I found out that the Roman tradition is more faithful to the the original story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, those who caused the Maidens of Flame to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:27.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Created a festival to commemorate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:31.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then unconsciously, it became the glorification of the maidens' sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth behind the Water Festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:10.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Sorry, I was thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about the Maidens of Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard from Naomi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:33.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been asking people about their dreams all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a wonderful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:47.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That even if I don't know what really happened before,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:58.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if this town and its citizens are here full of dreams, thanks to the Maidens of Flame, then it's just splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people aren't clear about the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they can vaguely feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:09.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're holding the festival with feelings of gratitude and guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The present exists because there's a past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:27.27,Sora Eng dialogue,Note 1,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also because the present exists that we can believe in tomorrow to pursue our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.77,Sora Eng dialogue,Note 1,0000,0000,0000,,A Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:37.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I still have something here for you, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:39.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:45.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san needs you to sign the receipt, otherwise, he can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, sorry to bother you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:52.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a princess, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even receiving a letter from the Emperor himself, that's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:02.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is coming to an end. Did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it, more or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, war is still raging.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:16.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, for now, there might be a temporary peace between Rome and Helvetia,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:23.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's also Gallia and the Franks next to Rome, and the western superpowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:27.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of country are still overshadowed by the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:31.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting each other to claim the few remaining land of the humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,reducing the already dwindling population!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining land...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first time seeing this, right? It's a world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been drawn in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:55.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there are undiscovered or unreachable areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:58.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there are plenty of places that are pure speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:08.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see this vast land... It was once the bulk of the Eurasia Continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:13.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has now become a death zone, a "no man's land".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:19.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, this "no man's land" is still expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Around Seize's border, the situation is still alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:29.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the north of Rome is continuously being eroded by the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:34.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's predicted that Rome will be completely engulfed by the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:44.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Rome by marriage and witnessed with my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:49.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the world is really doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:59.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should stop the war as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the world is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:08.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... That's your dream, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"To make the world peaceful."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would say, this is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in Misio's words,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"an objective."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about your dream, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-k-a-y!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing! Look at that, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:45.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemikaduchi's become so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first step of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:58.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was small, I heard from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:04.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere at the end of this world, there is an ocean of revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:07.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a piece of land that nurture new lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:10.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to seek that place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with this balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:15.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I would like to recreate an aeroplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:21.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The machine that helped man fly in the sky like birds in the old ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:29.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the world, or even further away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:34.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Further away from the end of the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a dream for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:39.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a rough blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:44.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day I will, step by step, make this dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:03.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's determine the Maiden of Flame of this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do it by lucky draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:07.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:11.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:15.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about doing it by Rock-paper-scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:16.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it in one turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:28.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:34.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You look nice, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:39.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's finish up the dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:42.39,Plate,Box,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\frz2.916\move(624,465,507,465)\frx54\fry6}For the Maiden of Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been here for a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:00.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time really flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:05.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai... I have decided on my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:11.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I be your follower forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:17.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we share the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:26.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:28.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.88,0:24:39.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Want to follow... my dream?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:42.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I've just written this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.05,0:24:43.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.87,0:24:52.88,Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\pos(652,405)\frz11.484}That I become a military doctor to save lots of lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.70,0:24:52.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to be a military doctor and save lots of lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.16,0:24:57.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, my elder sister was my idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.25,0:25:00.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:03.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:05.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was a medic...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.99,0:25:12.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Aisha was shot, I was so ashamed for not being able to lend a hand as my mom's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:15.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to do it, Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:16.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:23.91,Plate,Plate,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,469)\b}A lovely wife
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.51,0:25:23.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to be a lovely bride"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:39.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You will be able to do that, Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:44.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There must be someone who loves strange stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.27,0:25:46.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.66,0:25:50.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my own dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.34,0:25:52.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you written down?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.56,0:25:58.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote "I want to stay with you all forever."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.83,0:26:01.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dull...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.68,0:26:02.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.49,0:26:09.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that you will also be able to find yours and move forward someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.18,0:26:13.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream that only belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.72,0:26:20.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay. Until that day, I will hold your hand and walk alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.51,0:26:23.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you've found the dream meant only for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.90,0:26:28.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you start to play the music that belongs only to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.21,0:26:32.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:35.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The steps of a dream. The sound of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.09,0:26:37.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.79,0:26:40.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as I will be staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.14,0:26:43.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that you can come back from wherever you will go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.80,0:26:44.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.74,0:26:47.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.88,0:26:49.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:53.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! To the world we dream of!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.92,0:27:03.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world will be ruined one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.41,0:27:21.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before then, that's our future.
